{"tid":589367,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"玩家發明Switch最懶人玩法","createTime":"2018-03-11T23:45:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-12T03:40:10.000Z","uid":81228,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c480c4c675aeb238ca62ee8f0a654159abc2ce6a","tid":589367,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T23:45:29.000Z","msg":"任天堂Switch是一部充滿創意的遊戲機，這不僅僅體現在遊戲中，機器本身的玩法也非常多樣。而且它的分離式手掣，也給玩家們提供了極大的發揮空間。讓他們可以在官方介紹的正常方式之外，自己想一些創新玩法。<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.gameapps.hk/images/201803/11/m1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.gameapps.hk%2Fimages%2F201803%2F11%2Fm1.jpg&h=d64ce067&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最近，日本網友うきわ分享了一個Switch舒服玩法，那就是整個人都躺在床上，然後懶人支架掛著Swicth主機，兩手拿著Joy-Con手柄。雖然在旁人看來可能顯得有些「廢宅」，不過這樣的姿勢可以說是相當舒服了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.gameapps.hk/images/201803/11/m3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.gameapps.hk%2Fimages%2F201803%2F11%2Fm3.jpg&h=9469e71a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://image.gameapps.hk/images/201803/11/m2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.gameapps.hk%2Fimages%2F201803%2F11%2Fm2.jpg&h=58c3e784&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gameapps.hk/news/27357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gameapps.hk%2Fnews%2F27357&d=CVZBbZ0AGFcMBmKCtM2epMmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=528d065e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gameapps.hk/news/27357</a>"},{"pid":"de66d37d59644b2b74b477f12d78930565c60929","tid":589367,"uid":121868,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T00:15:41.000Z","msg":"ok喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a3dc2b41f90e953f4dc2ada904d728870f11611","tid":589367,"uid":48064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T00:56:46.000Z","msg":"就算係坐係度都可以抆個手制出黎垂低手玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好過傳統手制一舊過個膊要長期拗住<img src=\"/assets/fac